### CRM API

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3123

### Seed the database from the S3 CSV
POST {{baseUrl}}/seed

### --- Customers ---

### List all customers
GET {{baseUrl}}/customers

### Get a single customer
GET {{baseUrl}}/customers/DEMO43534060

### Get a customer's subscriptions
GET {{baseUrl}}/customers/1/subscriptions

### Get a customer's transactions
GET {{baseUrl}}/customers/1/transactions

### --- Subscriptions ---

### List all subscriptions
GET {{baseUrl}}/subscriptions

### Get a single subscription
GET {{baseUrl}}/subscriptions/1

### Get a subscription's transactions
GET {{baseUrl}}/subscriptions/1/transactions

### --- Transactions ---

### List all transactions
GET {{baseUrl}}/transactions

### Get a single transaction
GET {{baseUrl}}/transactions/1